<li>AraC family members often exist as dimers , joined by a dimerization surface in the N-terminal domain , whose activity may be regulated by ligand recognition .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12107132" target="_blank">12107132</a>]<br></li>
